Package: ETLDelphi
Title: Delphi/Delfi to OMOP CDM v5.4 ETL for DuckDB
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Adam", "Black", , "black@ohdsi.org", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5576-8701"))
  )
Maintainer: Adam Black <black@ohdsi.org>
Description: End-to-end ETL that transforms Delphi/Delfi source schema into
    OMOP Common Data Model v5.4 tables in DuckDB. Uses a 3-layer pattern
    (src -> stg -> cdm) with deterministic integer IDs and configurable
    concept mapping.
